- Markdown files in /content/ (except legal documents)
- Text content, blog posts, documentation
- Original images in /content/img/ and /public/img/
- Data files in /_data/

**Attribution Requirements:**
When using or sharing CC-BY-4.0 licensed content, you must:
- Give appropriate credit to "Fabian Fricke / LOD-AM Project"
